description: This Chainlink VRF hall of fame Gaston purrs with a rating of 62, and a multiplier of 5x. It has a total score of 310, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Leverage for North, Leverage for East, 1 for South, and Stringalong for West. Gaston has the personality suit of whale. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gaston [310 Votes, Hall of Fame]
